{"tid":1110946,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃子華說出大家心聲：鄭秀文與許志安是香港最後一個童話","createTime":"2019-04-16T18:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T18:33:38.000Z","uid":221586,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf2cf39f36190d8c041f0a58b83cb69f091dda7","tid":1110946,"uid":221586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"「今天，我想告訴鄭秀文，我要講的話是有社會意義的&hellip;&hellip;你（指鄭秀文）不要走，還不能走。為什麼全香港的人都希望你跟許志安在一起？因為&hellip;&hellip;你不用回答，因為這是一個童話！」全場發出歡呼聲。<br />\n<br />\n「我還沒有講完，金童玉女&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;曾經爆了，然後破鏡，竟然又能夠重圓。這個簡直就是童話中的童話，所以你明白嗎，這就是社會意義！今天的香港，已經沒有童話了！所以，你們在家裡吵架，如果許志安罵你，你是有權跟他說&mdash;&mdash;收聲！不是為了鄭秀文，而是為了香港！不要駁嘴，凡事以大局為重！」<br />\n<br />\n「問大家，這個童話怎樣可以最完美呢？生個兒子（全場又尖叫）！我連你兒子的名字都想好了，叫『許勝不許敗』，許志安的兒子，許勝不許敗，一家三口一起走出來，贏了！許志安，鄭秀文，許勝不許敗！」全場報以熱烈掌聲，鄭秀文隨即回應：「多謝！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/kknews.cc/entertainment/o3xybo.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fentertainment%2Fo3xybo.amp&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk8L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=c969d481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/kknews.cc/entertainment/o3xybo.amp</a>"},{"pid":"e1ef18aa6e7e501046004f02699450a1456760dc","tid":1110946,"uid":221586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3fe1f17cf72ae634d9b4ea6aa338fdd80fcbc7","tid":1110946,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:17:29.000Z","msg":"掛住子華神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abf25ade74d94636345202e27b6b5e2ae4d5756","tid":1110946,"uid":1834,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:24:12.000Z","msg":"啱啊，同童話一樣<br />\n係唔存在㗎"},{"pid":"06eadce946e84654308dd37e606e52984bd2a76e","tid":1110946,"uid":153524,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20